1
00:00:00,600 --> 00:00:03,320
Anything bothering you?

2
00:00:06,480 --> 00:00:08,480
Nothing in particular.

3
00:00:10,840 --> 00:00:12,400
I see.

4
00:00:12,400 --> 00:00:13,840
Glad to hear that.

5
00:00:14,360 --> 00:00:15,560
Please, stop it.

6
00:00:17,320 --> 00:00:18,480
- What's the big deal?
- Just for a second.

7
00:00:18,480 --> 00:00:20,280
Just a quick second, okay?

8
00:00:20,680 --> 00:00:22,320
I'm waiting for a friend...

9
00:00:22,560 --> 00:00:23,800
I said just a second!

10
00:00:23,800 --> 00:00:24,520
Please, don't!

11
00:00:24,520 --> 00:00:25,280
Hey, you guys!

12
00:00:25,280 --> 00:00:26,280
Idiots!

13
00:00:27,000 --> 00:00:29,840
She's my classmate!

14
00:00:29,840 --> 00:00:31,440
Let her go, will you?

15
00:00:32,200 --> 00:00:33,280
Iijima Hinata...

16
00:00:34,400 --> 00:00:36,280
What?

17
00:00:36,280 --> 00:00:37,840
Let go!

18
00:00:37,840 --> 00:00:39,000
That's enough.

19
00:00:40,720 --> 00:00:41,800
Who the hell are you?

20
00:00:43,480 --> 00:00:44,880
I'm his brother.

21
00:00:46,800 --> 00:00:49,280
Don't lie. You don't look like brothers at all.

22
00:00:49,680 --> 00:00:52,000
You want to get physical?

23
00:00:56,360 --> 00:00:58,800
You guys go to Shino High School, right?

24
00:00:59,760 --> 00:01:01,600
Even without your uniforms,

25
00:01:01,600 --> 00:01:02,920
it's obvious you're rich kids.

26
00:01:05,440 --> 00:01:06,440
How did you know?

27
00:01:06,920 --> 00:01:07,920
Your shoes!

28
00:01:09,080 --> 00:01:10,520
Those are the school-issued loafers.

29
00:01:13,760 --> 00:01:15,920
If you don't want me to report you,

30
00:01:18,440 --> 00:01:20,200
you'd better back off now.

31
00:01:26,360 --> 00:01:27,680
You're amazing.

32
00:01:27,680 --> 00:01:28,680
Thanks for your help.

33
00:01:29,600 --> 00:01:30,600
You idiot!
